# Slide 1: Title
Business Systems Readiness Assessment
Project Presentation

# Slide 2: Project Overview
- Branded, production-grade web app
- Personalized business pathway & PDF report
- Easy Artisan Websites branding
- API integration

# Slide 3: Key Features
- Responsive UI (Bootstrap)
- Interactive assessment form
- API integration for real-time results
- PDF report download
- Animated loading spinner
- Clear/reset answers and report

# Slide 4: Technology Stack
- Python 3, Flask (backend)
- HTML, CSS (Bootstrap), JavaScript (frontend)
- Jinja2 templating
- xhtml2pdf for PDF generation
- requests for API calls
- pytz for timezone handling

# Slide 5: Setup & Deployment
- Clone repository
- Create/activate virtual environment
- Install dependencies
- Run python app.py
- Access at http://localhost:5000

# Slide 6: Maintenance & Management
- Update dependencies via requirements.txt
- Update branding via static assets/index.html
- API changes: update API_URL and payload in app.py
- Edit pdf_report.html for PDF layout
- Replace spinner_2.gif for spinner updates

